Category:Imperial Navy pilots of the Galactic Empire

nodes.text: DS-75-5 was the call sign of an Imperial Navy TIE pilot who served by 0 BBY. During that year, the Alliance to Restore the Republic launched an attack on the Galactic Empire's DS-1 Orbital Battle Station. DS-75-5 was among the TIE pilots who partook in the subsequent battle, where numerous TIE/LN starfighters unsuccessfully attempted to defend the battlestation from the attacking Alliance starfighters. The space station was ultimately destroyed in an Alliance victory over the Empire.
DS-75-5 was created for 2008's The Complete Star Wars Encyclopedia.
